OL,3,CHundreds of children learn how to make
OL,4,Cthe perfect pancake
OL,6,FHundreds of schoolchildren from across
OL,7,Fhave come together to learn how to
OL,8,Fmake pancakes using local ingredients.
OL,10,FThe hands-on learning took place at
OL,11,Fthe county showground in where
OL,12,Fchildren had the chance to see, touch
OL,13,Fand taste local produce.
OL,15,FClare Morgan is a local poultry farmer
OL,16,Fwho brought some of her hens and their
OL,17,Feggs along to the event. She said: "To
OL,18,Fsee children's faces light up is
OL,19,Fabsolutely magical."
