OL,6,FShe added: "They don't realise how
OL,7,Fsilky a hen is going to feel, and
OL,8,Falso, how warm they are. And yesterday
OL,9,Fone of our girls laid an egg in front
OL,10,Fof the children from Hook School. So
OL,11,Fyou don't get much fresher than that."
OL,13,FEvent organiser, Katherine Wilson,
OL,14,Fsaid they've "had a lot of positive
OL,15,Fcomments from teachers."
OL,17,F"We've tried to link it into the new
OL,18,FWelsh curriculum." Katherine continued.
OL,20,F"I think it's purposeful. It's an
OL,21,Fauthentic day and experience for them.
