OL,6,F"We've got a multi-sensory approach
OL,7,Fwhere they're smelling things, they're
OL,8,Ftasting things, they're looking at
OL,9,Fthings, they're hearing things."
OL,11,FWalter Simon, from CLA Charitable
OL,12,FTrust, said: "It encompasses virtually
OL,13,Feverything that we do here, from cows
OL,14,Fand cereals to milk and cheese, and
OL,15,Fhoney. So it also covers the
OL,16,Fenvironment as well as productive
OL,17,Fagriculture."
